<TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=120 BGCOLOR="#DDDDDD"><FONT CLASS=GraphicCaption>"How about a server where I can't get my ass handed to me by a solo monk?"</FONT></TD>
<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><IMG SRC="images/spacer.gif"></TD>
